William Allan Smith-Masters, born William Allan Cowburn, (13 March 1850 – 27 August 1937) was an English cricketer.  Smith-Masters batting and bowling styles are unknown.  He was born in Humber, Herefordshire.
Smith-Masters made a single first-class appearance for Kent in 1875 against Hampshire at the Winchester College Ground, Winchester.  In his only first-class innings, Smith-Masters scored 7 runs.He died in Meopham, Kent on 27 August 1937.
